title: NCR Multi Purpose Ruled Duplicate Book A5 50 Sets Carbonless
features: Versatile Multi-Purpose Notebook: Ideal for various uses with ruled pages for neat and organized writing.
No Carbon Required (NCR) Paper: Ensures consistent, clear copies without the need for carbon paper.
Easy Removal: Top copy is perforated for effortless removal, while the bottom copy stays securely in the book.
Compact and Practical Design: A5 size (210mm x 148mm) with 50 sets of duplicates, complete with a loose-leaf writing shield.

Eco-Friendly Paper: As of 1.11.19, we use Carbon Balanced Paper in collaboration with the World Land Trust to reduce the carbon impact of our printed products, supporting environmental sustainability and climate change efforts.
